description:
Create schema extension API that wraps ai-database:

```typescript
import { DB } from '@dotdo/core'

// Use ai-database syntax
const schema = DB({
  Customer: {
    name: 'string',
    '-> orders': 'Order[]',
    '<~ industry': 'Industry',
  }
})

// Extend DO with schema
class MyDO extends DO.with(schema) { }
```

Also support:
- Zod schemas
- Direct Drizzle schemas for escape hatch

